# CyberShield AI — Multi-Agent Cyber Defense Platform

## Problem Understanding

Build a **smart cyber defense platform** that detects, analyzes, and explains emerging cyber threats using AI/ML. Threats: phishing, malicious URLs, deepfakes, prompt injection, anomalous behavior, AI-generated malicious content. The system must provide **explainability** (why something is flagged), **risk scoring**, and **actionable recommendations**.

## Architecture Refinement & Feedback

Your planned architecture is **strong** and covers all judging criteria. Here's my refined version with practical adjustments for the **2-hour constraint**:

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Key refinements from your original plan:**
> 1. **Google Safe Browsing API** for phishing URL detection (key confirmed ✅)
> 2. **Reality Defender API** for deepfake detection with 50 scans (key confirmed ✅)
> 3. **VirusTotal API** for malicious URL scanning (key confirmed ✅)
> 4. **SafePrompt API** → replaced with local prompt injection detector using pattern matching + Groq LLM scoring
> 5. **Simplify RAG** — use Groq LLM with structured context injection instead of full vector DB pipeline
> 6. **Add email parsing via `email` stdlib** — handles all email metadata extraction natively
> 7. **Adversarial testing** is a **bonus marks** goldmine (up to 10 marks) — input mutation + rescan

### Final Architecture Flow

```
Input Sources (Email/Message/URL/File)
        │
        ▼
┌─────────────────────────┐
│   Orchestrator Agent    │  ← Central coordinator
│   (FastAPI + async)     │
└────────┬────────────────┘
         │
    ┌────┴────────────────────────────────┐
    │  Content Extraction Agent           │
    │  (Email parser, URL extractor,      │
    │   file handler, text normalizer)    │
    └────────┬────────────────────────────┘
             │
    ┌────────┴──── Parallel Detection Agents ────────┐
    │                                                 │
    │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐            │
    │  │ Phishing     │  │ URL Scanner  │            │
    │  │ Detector     │  │ (VirusTotal) │            │
    │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘            │
    │  ┌──────────────┐  ┌──────────────┐            │
    │  │ Deepfake     │  │ Prompt Inj.  │            │
    │  │ Analyzer     │  │ Detector     │            │
    │  └──────────────┘  └──────────────┘            │
    │  ┌──────────────┐                              │
    │  │ Anomaly      │                              │
    │  │ Detector     │                              │
    │  └──────────────┘                              │
    └────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘
             │
    ┌────────┴────────────────────────────┐
    │  Cross-Validation Agent             │
    │  (Reduce false positives using      │
    │   local ML model consensus)         │
    └────────┬────────────────────────────┘
             │
    ┌────────┴────────────────────────────┐
    │  LLM Explainer Agent (Groq)         │
    │  + Context injection from threat    │
    │    intelligence (SERP API live)     │
    └────────┬────────────────────────────┘
             │
    ┌────────┴────────────────────────────┐
    │  Visual Breadcrumb Generator        │
    │  (Evidence highlighting, risk       │
    │   color coding, diff view)          │
    └────────┬────────────────────────────┘
             │
    ┌────────┴────────────────────────────┐
    │  Adversarial Testing Agent          │
    │  (Input mutation + rescan for       │
    │   robustness — BONUS MARKS)         │
    └────────────────────────────────────┘
```

