### Core Infrastructure

#### [NEW] [config.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/config.py)
- Environment-based config using `pydantic-settings`
- API keys: `VIRUSTOTAL_API_KEY`, `GROQ_API_KEY`, `SERP_API_KEY`
- Model settings, thresholds, feature flags

#### [NEW] [main.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/main.py)
- FastAPI application with CORS middleware (for future frontend)
- Include all routers
- Startup/shutdown events for initializing agents

#### [NEW] [requirements.txt](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/requirements.txt)
- `fastapi`, `uvicorn`, `pydantic`, `pydantic-settings`
- `httpx` (async HTTP), `python-multipart` (file uploads)
- `groq` (Groq SDK), `scikit-learn` (anomaly ML), `beautifulsoup4` (HTML parsing)
- `python-jose` (for future auth), `email-validator`

---

### Data Models (Schemas)

#### [NEW] [schemas.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/models/schemas.py)
- `ScanRequest` — input with source_type, content, metadata
- `ThreatDetection` — individual agent result with threat_type, confidence, evidence list
- `RiskScore` — composite risk with category breakdown
- `Breadcrumb` — visual evidence item with position, severity, description
- `ExplainerResult` — LLM explanation with reasoning chain
- `ScanResponse` — full response with all detections, explanations, recommendations
- `AdversarialResult` — mutation test results

---

### Agents

#### [NEW] [orchestrator.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/agents/orchestrator.py)
- Accepts `ScanRequest`, dispatches to content extractor
- Runs all relevant detection agents **in parallel** using `asyncio.gather`
- Pipes results through cross-validator, then LLM explainer
- Returns complete `ScanResponse`

#### [NEW] [content_extractor.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/agents/content_extractor.py)
- Parse raw email (`.eml`) using Python `email` stdlib
- Extract: sender, subject, body (plain + HTML), URLs, attachments metadata
- For messages: extract text + embedded URLs
- For URLs: fetch page content, extract metadata
- Output: `ExtractedContent` with all parsed fields

#### [NEW] [phishing_detector.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/agents/phishing_detector.py)
- **Google Safe Browsing API** integration for URL-level phishing checks
- Header analysis: SPF, DKIM, DMARC checks
- Urgency/social engineering pattern detection (NLP keyword scoring)
- Sender domain reputation check
- Link-text mismatch detection
- Outputs `ThreatDetection` with evidence points

#### [NEW] [url_scanner.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/agents/url_scanner.py)
- VirusTotal API v3 integration (`/urls` endpoint)
- URL reputation scoring from multiple engines
- Domain age check, redirect chain analysis
- Suspicious pattern detection (homograph attacks, IP-based URLs)

#### [NEW] [deepfake_analyzer.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/agents/deepfake_analyzer.py)
- **Reality Defender API** integration for deepfake detection (50 scans available)
- Metadata analysis of audio/video files as fallback
- Returns deepfake probability score + evidence from Reality Defender
- Outputs `ThreatDetection` with API-backed confidence

#### [NEW] [prompt_injection.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/agents/prompt_injection.py)
- Pattern-based detection (known injection patterns like "ignore previous", "system:", etc.)
- Structural analysis (unusual formatting, encoding tricks)
- LLM-based scoring via Groq for semantic injection detection

#### [NEW] [anomaly_detector.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/agents/anomaly_detector.py)
- IsolationForest model for user behavior scoring
- Feature extraction from login patterns (time, location, frequency)
- Statistical deviation scoring

#### [NEW] [cross_validator.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pilot/backend/agents/cross_validator.py)
- Takes all agent results, applies consensus scoring
- Reduces false positives via multi-signal correlation
- Adjusts confidence scores based on agreement/disagreement

---

### LLM Layer

#### [NEW] [explainer.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/llm/explainer.py)
- Groq API with `llama-3.3-70b-versatile`
- Structured prompting with detection results + enriched context
- Generates: human-readable explanation, reasoning chain, confidence justification
- Evidence-based explanation format with citations

#### [NEW] [context_enricher.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/llm/context_enricher.py)
- SERP API integration for live threat intelligence
- Known threat database context (curated patterns)
- Enriches detections with real-world context before LLM explaining

---

### Services

#### [NEW] [breadcrumb_generator.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/services/breadcrumb_generator.py)
- Generates visual breadcrumb data for frontend rendering
- Color-coded risk indicators (red/yellow/green)
- Position-aware evidence highlighting
- Diff-style consistency markers

#### [NEW] [adversarial_tester.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/services/adversarial_tester.py)
- Input mutation strategies: character substitution, unicode tricks, content rephrasing
- Re-scans mutated inputs through detection pipeline
- Reports robustness score + evasion attempts caught

