### API Endpoints

#### [NEW] [analyze.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/routers/analyze.py)
- `POST /api/analyze` — main scan endpoint (accepts JSON or file upload)
- `POST /api/analyze/email` — email-specific scan
- `POST /api/analyze/url` — URL-specific scan
- `POST /api/analyze/text` — text/message scan

#### [NEW] [health.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/routers/health.py)
- `GET /api/health` — system health + agent status

#### [NEW] [reports.py](file:///c:/Users/HP/Desktop/IndiaNext_Pixel_Pilots/backend/routers/reports.py)
- `GET /api/reports/{scan_id}` — fetch scan report
- `POST /api/reports/{scan_id}/adversarial` — trigger adversarial test

