## API Keys Required

> [!WARNING]
> **Set these API keys as environment variables (placeholders in `.env`):**
> - `VIRUSTOTAL_API_KEY` ✅ confirmed
> - `GOOGLE_SAFE_BROWSING_API_KEY` ✅ confirmed
> - `REALITY_DEFENDER_API_KEY` ✅ confirmed (50 scans)
> - `GROQ_API_KEY` — Free at [console.groq.com](https://console.groq.com)
> - `SERP_API_KEY` — Free tier at [serpapi.com](https://serpapi.com) (optional)

