| **Explainable AI (15)** | LLM-powered explanations with evidence chain, visual breadcrumbs, risk breakdown |
| **Cybersecurity Depth (15)** | SPF/DKIM/DMARC checks, VirusTotal integration, injection patterns, anomaly ML |
| **Innovation (10)** | Multi-agent orchestration, adversarial robustness testing, live threat intel |
| **Prototype Quality (10)** | Clean FastAPI with OpenAPI docs, structured JSON responses for PWA frontend |
| **Presentation (5)** | Architecture diagram, live demo-ready APIs |
| **BONUS (up to 10)** | Adversarial testing, privacy-aware design, real-time scoring |

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. **Run the server**: `.\venv\Scripts\python.exe -m uvicorn backend.main:app --reload --port 8000`
2. **Health check**: `curl http://localhost:8000/api/health`
3. **Test scan endpoint**: Send a phishing email sample via POST to `/api/analyze`
4. **Test URL scan**: POST a suspicious URL to `/api/analyze/url`
5. **Test prompt injection**: POST injection text to `/api/analyze/text`
6. **Verify OpenAPI docs**: Navigate to `http://localhost:8000/docs` in browser

### Manual Verification
- Verify all API responses match Pydantic schemas
- Verify parallel agent execution completes within reasonable time
- Test with real phishing email samples from public datasets
